{
  "stem": "13395.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It is the property of the post office.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He brought it back to camp and showed it to the commander.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They opened the letter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she read it, and she knew it was my letter.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she called me in and showed me the letter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all I wrote in that letter was to my aunt that I cannot write to my mother, but I know that she's worried.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she took that letter and took that Judenalteste with her and went to the city to the SS headquarters.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And said to the commander there, to the oberscharfuhrer, that she has somebody in her camp that has stepped out of bound.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that she'd like him to send her away to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this commander says, so what should she do?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, well, she sent a letter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, show me the letter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He reads the letter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The reason I know the story is because the Judenalteste was with her, and then she told me what happened.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says to her, woman, what do you want to do to this child?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All she wants is her mother to know that she is alive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Is that a crime?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "For this, you want to send her to Auschwitz?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Go back to your camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I only know it because the Judenalteste was with her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So here you have a peculiar situation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "An SS officer, a Nazi-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a second time-- is acting humanely.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So if we say that they were crazy or they were deranged to do what they did to the Jews, it's very difficult to say this.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were human.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The only thing was they followed the orders of a vicious leadership.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But deep inside, some of them had some humanity left.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
